{"tid":2337291,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"關於lm狗單嘢，有啲嘢必須要澄清一下。","createTime":"2020-12-23T07:45:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-23T08:39:26.000Z","uid":343520,"like":11,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"287ae1ac7a1c7618bfea90befead2abdcd428922","tid":2337291,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T07:45:03.000Z","msg":"今日見到好多人將木耳同lm狗拉埋黎講，我唔知呢班人係弱智fans定係冇認知能力，<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">將風向spin到波台眼紅人起人底</span></strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但唔該留意返佢兩個係完全唔同嘅situation 嚟，我亦都冇因為佢畫弱智圖上到位而不滿，我講過好多次，百貨應百客，佢有受眾而紅左，係一啲問題都冇。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先，木耳係同人無仇無怨，因為唔小心自爆左，只係自己一時柒左，對於呢個情況，我係100%同情，唔會落井下石嘅。<br />\n<br />\n而<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">LM狗係行為狗公，發情隨便騷擾女性</span></strong></span>，如果咁都冇人指出，遲下係咪個個有錢有小小名氣就可以唔尊重女性？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>覺得我講錯嘅，自己睇</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/knVwRUc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FknVwRUc.png&h=c0cc9364&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>請問下LM狗，你可以解釋下咩叫重酬未呢？</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n你係街見到靚女食飯就鳩痕，周圍開po、開ig尋人我都算喇，最多當你係痴線佬，但你依家係講到明重酬喎，<span class=\"red\"><strong><span class=\"x-large\">用利益誘使人做出不道德行為喎。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n依家人地食個飯咋喎，同你又咩關係都冇，你重酬尋人算係咩意思？江湖追殺令呀？<br />\n<br />\n咁如果有人為左錢而真係去用任何方法搵個女仔出黎，為左錢而去騷擾呢位女士，有冇諗過會對人地造成影響呀？<br />\n<br />\n人地食個飯就要比你件狗公騷擾？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>麻煩LM狗呢次唔好再扮睇唔到，做返個男人啦，你一係出黎解釋，一係同人道歉。</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"af0794a600bae98fcce3c92ac2a053c5954de951","tid":2337291,"uid":23655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T07:45:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f34100c1060045bc37a9279f66a0e0bcbed19462","tid":2337291,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T07:46:35.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">咪扮睇唔到，我屌你老母！</span>"},{"pid":"a3beac90b4188f585eceebd7624d1da4c83c8cec","tid":2337291,"uid":367153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T07:46:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c740b10626b71ed214f36f6aae8b204eed0338d","tid":2337291,"uid":241543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T07:47:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf6fd1dd2917ceee0a044c8a9c6f81f558934fdc","tid":2337291,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T07:48:27.000Z","msg":"條撚屌連正面回應都唔敢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5561e152c27c0a4fb0e47d9ab3b87ecca649cd6b","tid":2337291,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T07:49:07.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>出黎面對啦LM狗賊！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"5de153506e100aac9b9cfd88064b61898061f6ab","tid":2337291,"uid":120729,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T07:49:48.000Z","msg":"喺條街冒住自爆嘅風險幫你推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b3dd742400b73a640d362d70cb598843cb9db60","tid":2337291,"uid":23655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5de153506e100aac9b9cfd88064b61898061f6ab","tid":2337291,"uid":120729,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T07:49:48.000Z","msg":"喺條街冒住自爆嘅風險幫你推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1